data.description: Well cared for 3 bed 2 bath home sitting on 1.3 acres in Northwestern school district. Walking in the front door brings you to the living room with dining to your right. Straight ahead is 2 bedrooms and a full bath with. Walking through the living room will bring you to the owners suit which features a large bathroom with a corner tub. Walking back out through the living room, passed the dining you will find the kitchen and another flex living space.
